/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.148469413374705e-38, \"text\": \"TikTok\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/TikTok\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Christiansen ranked the dessert, baked by French catering company Coup de Pates, an 11/10 on the social media platform and raved about them.\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 629, \"end\": 635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9480465207519514, \"rank\": 0.054787401594481644, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old and said they were not only \\\"insane\\\" but \\\"the single greatest thing about the Olympics so far\\\".\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are very rich, and I like that,\\\" he told the New York Times.\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 893, \"end\": 901, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999940039288, \"rank\": 5.9780374704735856e-09, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a lot of misconception regarding athletes and what they eat - of course, some athletes, they do sports where their weight is carefully watched and it's a lot more important.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 1093, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On my most heavy training days, I can get up to almost 7000 calories a day.\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1171, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's tough to have that many calories if you are only having salad.\", \"from\": 